# DC Scan volunteer board

Skill: `.cursor/skills/dc-scan-volunteer-board/SKILL.md` (read before edits).  
Allowlist / access requests: `access-and-allowlist.md`. Supervisor email: `supervisor-notify.md`.

## URLs

- UI: `https://the-dump-bin.com/dc-scan/` (`the-dump-bin/dc-scan/index.html`)
- API: `https://eod-api.the-dump-bin.com/api/dc-scan/`
- eod-api `/dc-scan` only **redirects** to dump-bin — do not treat `src/public/dc-scan/` as canonical.

## Claimed ≠ In PROD

- **In PROD** / **Completed** badges require `liveProd.ok` and `prodConfirmsInProd()` — not stored `sasVisitId`, not seed `buildStatus`.
- Completed SAS visit/shift status counts as PROD-confirmed.

## SAS PROD sync

- `sasBridge.init()` **before** `initDcScanBoard()` and `startDcScanProdSync()`.
- Poll uses `dc-scan-sas-sync.js`; resync via `POST /api/dc-scan/resync`.
- Store matching: `lib/sas-store-match.js` only — never trust `store_number=` API filter alone.

## Volunteer allowlist

Dump Bin sign-in ≠ DC Scan claim access. Use `alternateEmails`, `DC_SCAN_VOLUNTEER_EMAILS`, or access-request approval (`dc_scan_volunteer_grants`).

## Deploy

Push **both** `eod-api` and `the-dump-bin` before Railway/Pages redeploy. Set `DC_SCAN_APPROVER_EMAIL=tyson.gauthier@retailodyssey.com` on Railway.
